name: Quantum Outsourcing
overview:
Where

Headquartered and incorporated in Romania, we are a leading IT solutions provider offering a multitude of high quality development and support services to our global clientele encompassing various industry verticals like fashion, finance, catering, and many more. We successfully cater to markets across the globe including USA, United Kingdom, Australia, Canada, Israel, New Zealand and many more.

What

We offer a comprehensive range of effective web and software solutions backed by powerful design intelligence, innovative methodologies, agile project management, and a flexible delivery model. With a strong hold on latest technologies, our team of highly expert IT professionals is able to deliver innovative solutions tailored to your business needs.

Who

We are a team of highly skilled professionals brought together and connected by our passion for IT. Our team boasts of domain knowledge, effective methodologies, technical skills, vast industry experience, and above all, zeal for what we do! Our IT specialists will help you at each step of achieving even your most ambitious objectives.
